        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How do Tsarbomba's interchangeable bezels work?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tsarbomba's patented system uses a snap-on mechanism that requires no tools. You simply align the bezel and press it into place, making swaps quick and easy for any occasion.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Are Tsarbomba watches suitable for everyday wear?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. They're crafted with durable materials like carbon fiber and titanium, resistant to scratches and corrosion, combined with Swiss movements for reliability in daily activities.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can I buy additional bezel sets for my Tsarbomba watch?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes, Tsarbomba offers standalone bezel sets in various materials and colors, allowing you to expand your customization options beyond the initial watch purchase.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
